              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The thickness-corrected relative cross sections were",
                "normalized for 5.07 mb/sr at Ed=0.901MeV.",
                "This calibration is based on the average value of the",
                "cross sections of 4.40 mb/sr at 135. degr. and",
                "5.75 mb/sr at 165. degr., since there is no data",
                "available at 150. degr. for the reaction.",
                "See, J.R.Tesmer,M.Nastasi (Eds.), Handbook of Modern",
                "Ion Beam Materials Analysis, Materials Research",
